{"tid":1090172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為同志兒代孕產女 美婦既是母親又是祖母","createTime":"2019-04-03T09:36:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-03T12:48:40.000Z","uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5b136a9a08717b75f09f767a75e43e050d0b1a9c","tid":1090172,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T09:36:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190403/_2019040316302538827.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190403%2F_2019040316302538827.jpg&h=eaf0f497&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國內布拉斯加州一名61歲母親為自己的同性戀兒子當代母，早前為兒子和兒子的同性伴侶誕下女兒，亦同時為自己添個孫女。<br />\n<br />\n這名叫艾萊德格（Cecile Eledge）的產婦說，她得知自己的兒子馬修（Matthew Eledge）和同性伴侶多爾蒂（Elliot Dougherty）想要一個孩子時，就主動提出為他們當代母。她上星期成功產下一名女嬰，取名烏馬（Uma）。<br />\n<br />\n多爾蒂形容，最初聽到母親的建議時，覺得是個「十分美好」的想法，形容她是「無私的女性」，但這並非一帆風順的過程。對一般異性夫婦來說，人工授孕是無法透過正常方法懷孕時最後的方法，但對同性戀伴侶，人工授孕是產下孩子的唯一辦法。艾萊德格說，她提出為兒子當代母時，家人都覺得只是一個笑話，沒有認真看待。但馬修和多爾蒂徵詢過家庭科醫生後，發現母親的確可以為他們當代母，代為產下孩子。<br />\n<br />\n艾萊德格接受連串測試後，醫生批准她當代母。<span style=\"color: red;\">精子由馬修捐出，多爾蒂的姐姐萊亞（Lea）捐出卵子，之後將受孕的胚胎植入到艾萊德格的子宮。</span>艾萊德格說，烏馬出生一個星期以來健康良好，也將會在一個充滿愛的家庭成長。而烏馬的出世證明書也只有艾萊德格和馬修的名字，沒有多爾蒂的名字。這是因為當地法律訂明，證明書內「母親」一欄寫的必須是誕兒的人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190403/_2019040316302629426.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190403%2F_2019040316302629426.jpg&h=db87ebe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190403/_2019040316302624745.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190403%2F_2019040316302624745.jpg&h=06b1638b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/972128\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F972128&d=oUHbLHmoFTyfHyZ%2Brcpj5IZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=a25ab8e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F972128&h=356eeaf0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/972128</a>"},{"pid":"640d988e4d9f14cceab0554364a0c95542c5d43f","tid":1090172,"uid":195570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T09:40:47.000Z","msg":"個仔出世之前仲可以繼續瘋狂屌屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18e2c15994a87b3d30a7f5b1f11853717f118cfc","tid":1090172,"uid":1149,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T09:47:35.000Z","msg":"全新槪念亂倫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d05fa5ff8875b537872d28fdd37f1d509865152","tid":1090172,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T09:53:52.000Z","msg":"瘋狂嘅世界"},{"pid":"0caa2647e21c179d05c87d4844da729371e9c87b","tid":1090172,"uid":22362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T11:47:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72bf15b7c9743bfe9903bcf60e0ca08ac32fd9e4","tid":1090172,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T11:51:39.000Z","msg":"點派利是？"},{"pid":"86b69601d47d2805008057f5dbf26d1658adb227","tid":1090172,"uid":185953,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T11:52:57.000Z","msg":"咁多位早晨，我今日嚟，係想同你哋講個故事嘅：<br />\n<br />\n喺幾年前<br />\n我同一個寡婦結咗婚<br />\n佢有一個已成年嘅女<br />\n後來嫁咗比我老豆<br />\n<br />\n咁我繼女就做咗我後媽<br />\n而我老豆就做咗我女婿<br />\n<br />\n兩年後我老婆同我生咗一個仔<br />\n佢喺我後媽嘅同母異父嘅細佬<br />\n我個仔叫我「老豆」<br />\n我就叫我個仔「舅父」<br />\n<br />\n我繼女又為我老豆生咗一個仔<br />\n佢喺我細佬<br />\n但佢又要叫我外公<br />\n<br />\n我喺我老婆個老公<br />\n但喺我老婆喺我後媽個阿媽喎<br />\n所以我喺自己嘅外公<br />\n<br />\n到咗新年<br />\n嚟料喇<br />\n<br />\n我就同我後媽同我老豆<br />\n即係同我繼女同女婿交換利是<br />\n<br />\n我封廿蚊比我個仔<br />\n佢話：「多謝老豆！」<br />\n我又答返佢：「唔洗，舅父！喺呢，咁我嗰封呢？」<br />\n「你都痴線，我結咗婚喇咩？」唉，我自己都亂咗... <br />\n<br />\n食團年飯嗰陣<br />\n我喺抬面上面放咗一封一千蚊利是<br />\n再拎返封利是上手<br />\n叫咗聲：「多謝外公！」<br />\n<br />\n好彩唔喺街姐<br />\n唔係真係比人捉去青山瞓一排<br />\n而家諗返自己真喺痴痴地線<br />\n自己比錢自己洗<br />\n咪即係去自己鋪頭買野..."},{"pid":"09e4ad42e6146f6e72d0b99dba02e69cf2a39101","tid":1090172,"uid":121546,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T11:55:36.000Z","msg":"可能亂倫先係真,同性戀係掩飾"},{"pid":"66eceebb4fefbc08698cc2973e49aa67a9643e76","tid":1090172,"uid":246353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09e4ad42e6146f6e72d0b99dba02e69cf2a39101","tid":1090172,"uid":121546,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T11:55:36.000Z","msg":"可能亂倫先係真,同性戀係掩飾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T12:42:24.000Z","msg":"代理出產の母<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pornhub.com/view_video.php?viewkey=ph5b0da19ac68e7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pornhub.com%2Fview_video.php%3Fviewkey%3Dph5b0da19ac68e7&d=oUHbLHmoFTyfHyZ%2Brcpj5IZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=fe69fb39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pornhub.com/view_video.php?viewkey=ph5b0da19ac68e7</a><br />\n代理出産の母 本庄ひとみ"},{"pid":"9ac098c6ecee1ccad1beb5879e45f8deb7522886","tid":1090172,"uid":74326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T12:48:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}